A Simple REST API Demonstrating Social Networking Site, having twi Entity
User and Post.
A User can have several Posts having One To Many Relationship.

TOPICS:
GET,POST,DELETE
SpringJPA
Validations of RESTful Services(Java Validation API)
HATEOS
SWAGGER
Content Negotiation
Static Filtering and Dynamic Filtering
Springboot Actuator
Versioning
Basic Authentication with Springboot
Exception Handling techniques in Springboot


More Info:
Launch the application by running RestfulWebServicesApplication.Java
Hit:
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html : To See all Information

Above info can also be accesed by below url
http://localhost:8080/v2/api-docs
